column5: Nice carp and cats Rich!  Thanks for sharing, you guys do well with the bottom feeders  Big crappie too!  MTBF
nice fish it looks like you are getting a good start on the year.   Art
Thought the mirror carp was a catfish at first due to lack of scales. Keep on fishin BBR.
Nice!!!  Them cats got a face only a mama could love!
You've been doing well. Great pics! Thats a great looking mirror
Sweet. We've seen a few mirrors lately. In some of the pics it looks like you are in the bayou.
Close!  lol  Nice fish mon friere!
Man there's some ugliness in that post!!!  Good to see you out young lad!
Was thinking the same thing Wayne.  Faces only a mother could love!  Great job Rich!
im now scared to ever go into the water again ...
